        </item>
        <item>
            <title>Google Gboard 推真「Key CAPS」  敲击脑袋打字</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2023/10/07/google-gboard-keycaps/life-tech/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=google-gboard-keycaps</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2023/10/07/google-gboard-keycaps/life-tech/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Sat, 07 Oct 2023 06:34:47 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[生活科技]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Gboard]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Gboard CAPS]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1197875</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>日本 Google 每年都会推出与 Google 键盘（Gboard）有关的恶搞影片，今年日本 Google 则推出了「Gboard CAPS」「键帽」。</p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1197889" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Gboard-CAPS-0-19-screenshot-694x390.png" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Gboard-CAPS-0-19-screenshot-694x390.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Gboard-CAPS-0-19-screenshot-1280x720.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Gboard-CAPS-0-19-screenshot-768x432.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Gboard-CAPS-0-19-screenshot-1536x864.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Gboard-CAPS-0-19-screenshot.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1197885" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Gboard-CAPS-0-32-screenshot-694x390.png" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Gboard-CAPS-0-32-screenshot-694x390.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Gboard-CAPS-0-32-screenshot-1280x720.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Gboard-CAPS-0-32-screenshot-768x432.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Gboard-CAPS-0-32-screenshot-1536x864.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Gboard-CAPS-0-32-screenshot.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1197888" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Gboard-CAPS-0-21-screenshot-694x390.png" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Gboard-CAPS-0-21-screenshot-694x390.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Gboard-CAPS-0-21-screenshot-1280x720.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Gboard-CAPS-0-21-screenshot-768x432.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Gboard-CAPS-0-21-screenshot-1536x864.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Gboard-CAPS-0-21-screenshot.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>今年推出的 Gboard CAPS 实际上就是一顶和键盘上的键帽（Keycap）一模一样的帽子。据日本 Google 表示，这顶 Gboard CAPS 内置陀螺仪，用家打字时只需面向不同方向，CAPS 就可以侦测用家想打甚么字符，最后轻敲头部就可以用蓝牙传输结果至电脑、手机等。日本 Google 称这种输入法为「Atama Input」，意即「头脑输入」。</p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1197887" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Gboard-CAPS-0-25-screenshot-694x390.png" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Gboard-CAPS-0-25-screenshot-694x390.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Gboard-CAPS-0-25-screenshot-1280x720.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Gboard-CAPS-0-25-screenshot-768x432.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Gboard-CAPS-0-25-screenshot-1536x864.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Gboard-CAPS-0-25-screenshot.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲CAPS 内置陀螺仪</p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1197886" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Gboard-CAPS-0-26-screenshot-694x390.png" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Gboard-CAPS-0-26-screenshot-694x390.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Gboard-CAPS-0-26-screenshot-1280x720.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Gboard-CAPS-0-26-screenshot-768x432.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Gboard-CAPS-0-26-screenshot-1536x864.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Gboard-CAPS-0-26-screenshot.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲能够侦测用家方向，从而知悉用家想打甚么字</p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1197884" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Gboard-CAPS-0-34-screenshot-694x390.png" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Gboard-CAPS-0-34-screenshot-694x390.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Gboard-CAPS-0-34-screenshot-1280x720.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Gboard-CAPS-0-34-screenshot-768x432.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Gboard-CAPS-0-34-screenshot-1536x864.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Gboard-CAPS-0-34-screenshot.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲再以蓝牙传输至你的装置</p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1197883" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Gboard-CAPS-0-11-screenshot-694x390.png" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Gboard-CAPS-0-11-screenshot-694x390.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Gboard-CAPS-0-11-screenshot-1280x720.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Gboard-CAPS-0-11-screenshot-768x432.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Gboard-CAPS-0-11-screenshot-1536x864.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Gboard-CAPS-0-11-screenshot.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>日本 Google 更表示 CAPS 可以选择不同机械轴，例如青轴、茶轴、红轴键盘版本。其更表示这种声波可以刺激脑部发展，对智商有莫大脾益。除此之外，CAPS 更可为用家遮风挡雨。</p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1197891" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Gboard-CAPS-0-47-screenshot-694x390.png" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Gboard-CAPS-0-47-screenshot-694x390.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Gboard-CAPS-0-47-screenshot-1280x720.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Gboard-CAPS-0-47-screenshot-768x432.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Gboard-CAPS-0-47-screenshot-1536x864.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Gboard-CAPS-0-47-screenshot.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>有用家表示一直寻找头戴式键盘，但苦无结果。他表示使用 CAPS 后感觉非常方便，他又指用家可以轻松装备这顶帽子。</p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1197892" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Gboard-CAPS-1-8-screenshot-694x390.png" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Gboard-CAPS-1-8-screenshot-694x390.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Gboard-CAPS-1-8-screenshot-1280x720.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Gboard-CAPS-1-8-screenshot-768x432.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Gboard-CAPS-1-8-screenshot-1536x864.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Gboard-CAPS-1-8-screenshot.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1197893" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Gboard-CAPS-1-11-screenshot-694x390.png" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Gboard-CAPS-1-11-screenshot-694x390.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Gboard-CAPS-1-11-screenshot-1280x720.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Gboard-CAPS-1-11-screenshot-768x432.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Gboard-CAPS-1-11-screenshot-1536x864.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Gboard-CAPS-1-11-screenshot.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>虽然这顶帽子听起来非常有趣，但即使你对它非常有兴趣也没有用，因为这顶帽和早前「Gboard BAR」一样，只是一个玩笑，不会真的公开发售。</p><p>资料来源：<a href="https://tw.news.yahoo.com/googlgboard-caps-032829171.html">Yahoo 新闻</a>、<a href="https://landing.google.co.jp/caps/">Google</a>、<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6vib77CUxNM&amp;ab_channel=GoogleJapan">YouTube</a></p><h2> 最新影片</h2><div class="video-container"><iframe loading="lazy" title="最新影片" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/videoseries?list=PLiEPZioiGtHw9_9gm4Ty0_pTEviOKNvfl" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></div></p>
]]>
            </description>
            <wfw:commentRss>https://unwire.hk/2023/10/07/google-gboard-keycaps/life-tech/feed/</wfw:commentRss>
